long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Hoody Privacy Manager is a powerful browser extension that allows you to easily manage and switch between various zero-log SOCKS5 proxies for enhanced privacy and security. Plus, with our advanced browser spoofing feature, you can virtually change your browser type, version, and operating system.

🛡️ Bulletproof Proxies:
For the ultimate privacy, our Bulletproof Proxies assign a new random IP for every request you make. Available in 5 regions for optimal latency:
- 🌎 World (Random IPs all over the world)
- 🌎 North America
- 🌏 Asia 
- 🇪🇺 Europe 
- 🧅 Tor (Your IP will be a Tor Exit node)

🎁 Free Proxies (Limited to 1MB/s, NO SIGNUP NEEDED):
- 🇭🇰 Hong Kong
- 🇳🇱 Netherlands (Amsterdam)
- 🇺🇸 United States (Miami)

🌟Premium Proxies (+45 locations - Uncapped, 10Gbit/s, ANONYMOUS REGISTRATION):
See complete list at https://hoody.com/dashboard/proxies 

🔒 Always Double-Hop:
All proxies are always double-hop, with 9 regions for the first hop, automatically selected via DNS.

🌐 New Feature: Browser Spoofing
Choose among 100+ browsers and OS. Easily spoof your browser's user agent and JS parameters to further mask your fingerprints and prevent tracking.

🛡️ WebRTC Blocking:
Hoody Proxy Manager also offers a built-in feature to block WebRTC on all websites, providing an additional layer of privacy protection.

🔒 Absolutely ZERO LOGS
Servers run on RAMDisk with initramfs, ensuring no logs are stored, our architecture ensures that we cannot access or monitor any user data or traffic passing through our network.

Discover all our Privacy products, Per-App VPN, Browsing Containers and more at hoody.com
